6.01	Fist_of_legend	Fist of Legend	Fist of Legend is a 1994 Hong Kong martial arts action film directed by Gordon Chan and features action choreography by Yuen Woo-ping, and also produced by and starring Jet Li. It is a remake of the 1972 film Fist of Fury, which starred Bruce Lee as the lead character. The film is set in Shanghai International Settlement in 1937 during the Second Sino-Japanese War as the city is occupied by Japanese forces.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/8/80/FistOfLegend.Jpg/220px-FistOfLegend.Jpg
